I`ve downloaded your stuff, but I`cant watch it. It needs some sort of licence key, what`s up with that?
dude go to download.cnet.com and download the cccp or ccp its something like the the codec must be missin or something
75 Mb ??? Dude why bother torrenting a trailer? Ever heard of youtube?

Maybe someone would like to own the trailer, like myself.

Thanks for the up EZ

This torrent will disappear as soon as the movie is available. In the meantime, we can assume its existence serves two purposes.

1) To alert users that extremezone is aware of the Pirates of the Caribbean 4 movie and will be uploading it themselves when the time comes;

and

2) To provide users with a full size trailer to wet their appetites. For those who never pay for movies, extremezone is doing the job of the movie theater marketing teams. For the rest of us, its pretty much worthless.

It is what it is. Can't wait to download the full length movie, extremezone. Keep up the good work.
